name: Mens Tees
description:
Our all time most popular artwork is now available on a T-shirt!

All of our T-shirts are full colour screen printed. We use Gildan 175-185g/m² preshrunk, 100% Jersey Cotton T-Shirts which are a great quality, heavy shirt. 

Our tees are NOT colour transfers but professional full colour CYMK screen prints using the latest technology to ensure bold, crisp results and a T-Shirt that will last. 

Please use the size guide below to choose your perfect fit.

Small: 34/36"  Medium: 38/40"  Large 42/44"  XLarge: 46/48"

name: GIFT VOUCHERS
description:
If you are not sure which product to buy for a gift let a voucher make life easier! Or, if you have left it too late to place an order, a voucher is an instant way to buy a gift.

Simply select the value of the voucher you would like and pay online. We will then email you a unique code which will discount the voucher amount at the store check out. The email containing the voucher code will be sent within 30 minutes of the order being placed. 

The voucher is sent in digital format so nothing will be posted to you, but you can print the voucher yourself if you want to put it in an envelope etc for a gift. The voucher is valid for one year and can be used as part payment in any order within the CTM store.
